item.title: CVE-2022-36898|2024-08-03T10:14:29.369Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20compuware%20ispw%20operations%20plugin
item.description: A missing permission check in Jenkins Compuware ISPW Operations Plugin 1.0.8 and earlier allows attackers with Overall/Read permission to enumerate hosts and ports of Compuware configurations and credentials IDs of credentials stored in Jenkins.

item.title: CVE-2022-36899|2024-08-03T10:14:29.353Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20compuware%20ispw%20operations%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Compuware ISPW Operations Plugin 1.0.8 and earlier does not restrict execution of a controller/agent message to agents, allowing attackers able to control agent processes to retrieve Java system properties.
